OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny overnight rain soon
OL,6,Fclearing east. Otherwise cooler and
OL,7,Fmainly cloudy with some patchy light
OL,8,Fdrizzle possible, but west coast
OL,9,Fbrightening up with some warm sunshine
OL,10,Fbreaking out.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will stay dull and cloudy
OL,13,Fin the east overnight. Variable cloud
OL,14,Fand sunny then clear spells in the
OL,15,Fwest through the evening and
OL,16,Fovernight. Staying dry.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
