OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FA largely cloudy start, but
OL,6,Fbright around the west coast and
OL,7,FWestern Isles. Brightening up through
OL,8,Fthe day with sunny intervals
OL,9,Fdeveloping for all. Warm, very warm in
OL,10,Fthe west.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FA dry
OL,13,Ffew days with good spells of sunshine
OL,14,Fat times, especially Monday. Very warm
OL,15,Fin the west with the best of the
OL,16,Fsunshine, cloudier at times in the
OL,17,Feast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
